OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1774638672
OL,3,CRedundancies and service changes
OL,4,Cannounced at Isle of Man's only hospice
OL,6,FThe only hospice service on the Isle
OL,7,Fof Man has announced redundancies and
OL,8,Fchanges to its services, as it says
OL,9,Fits "financial reality is increasingly
OL,10,Funstable".
OL,12,FHospice Isle of Man said a combination
OL,13,Fof increasing costs, an aging
OL,14,Fpopulation and only 24% of its funding
OL,15,Fcoming from the Government had meant
OL,16,Fit had been operating at a deficit for
OL,17,Fthe past six years.
OL,19,FIt was not a position it could
OL,20,Fmaintain, it said, "without risking
OL,21,Fthe long-term future of the charity".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1774638672
OL,3,CRedundancies and service changes
OL,4,Cannounced at Isle of Man's only hospice
OL,6,FIn a statement the hospice added: "As
OL,7,Fa result, we have had to make the very
OL,8,Fdifficult decision to reduce our cost
OL,9,Fbase, refocus our services and stop
OL,10,Ffilling gaps in the wider healthcare
OL,11,Fsystem.
OL,13,F"This means there will be changes to
OL,14,Fsome of our services and redundancies
OL,15,Ffor some of our employees.
OL,17,F"Throughout this process, we will
OL,18,Fprioritise protecting our core
OL,19,Fservices, our in-patient unit, Hospice
OL,20,Fat Home and Rebecca House Children's
OL,21,FHospice."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1774638672
OL,3,CRedundancies and service changes
OL,4,Cannounced at Isle of Man's only hospice
OL,6,FIt added: "This is a sad moment for
OL,7,FHospice care on our island, but also a
OL,8,Fnecessary step to protect Hospice care
OL,9,Ffor future generations.
OL,11,F"We are committed to supporting our
OL,12,Fstaff through this change, and our
OL,13,Fpatients for years to come."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1774638672
OL,3,CRedundancies and service changes
OL,4,Cannounced at Isle of Man's only hospice
OL,6,FThe charity said its ability to
OL,7,Fprovide "compassionate, specialist
OL,8,Fcare to hundreds of patients and their
OL,9,Ffamilies" had previously only been
OL,10,Fmade possible because of the
OL,11,F"extraordinary generosity of the Manx
OL,12,Fpublic" through donations, fundraising
OL,13,Fand community support.
OL,15,FBut, due to funding constraints -
OL,16,Fwhere it claimed the Manx Government
OL,17,Fonly provided 24% of the charity's
OL,18,Ftotal income compared to 44% in Jersey
OL,19,Fand an average of 36% in the UK - it
OL,20,Fhad been forced to make the "difficult
OL,21,Fdecision".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1774638672
OL,3,CRedundancies and service changes
OL,4,Cannounced at Isle of Man's only hospice
OL,6,F"We fully recognise the impact this
OL,7,Fwill have on our dedicated staff,
OL,8,Fvolunteers, and the wider community we
OL,9,Fserve", the statement continued.
OL,11,F"These changes are being made to
OL,12,Fensure we can continue to provide
OL,13,Fcompassionate care, dignity, and
OL,14,Fclinical excellence for those in the
OL,15,Ffinal weeks of life, now and into the
OL,16,Ffuture."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1774638672
OL,3,CRedundancies and service changes
OL,4,Cannounced at Isle of Man's only hospice
OL,6,FIt added the hospice will continue to
OL,7,Fcollaborate closely with the
OL,8,FGovernment and Manx Care, but will now
OL,9,Fbe launching a campaign,
OL,10,F_FairFundingHospiceIOM, to ensure it
OL,11,Fcan continue into the future.
OL,13,FIn response to the news, the
OL,14,FDepartment of Health and Social Care
OL,15,Fand Manx Care, said patients and
OL,16,Ffamilies "can be reassured they will
OL,17,Fcontinue to receive the hospice care
OL,18,Fthey rely on".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1774638672
OL,3,CRedundancies and service changes
OL,4,Cannounced at Isle of Man's only hospice
OL,6,FIt added it was working closely with
OL,7,Fthe charity to ensure care continues
OL,8,Fand a "full review" of commissioning
OL,9,Farrangements will be delivered by
OL,10,FSeptember.
OL,12,F"The Department of Health and Social
OL,13,FCare (DHSC) and Manx Care recognise
OL,14,Fthe financial pressures facing Hospice
OL,15,Fand support its focus on core
OL,16,Fpalliative and end-of-life care," its
OL,17,Fstatement said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1774638672
OL,3,CRedundancies and service changes
OL,4,Cannounced at Isle of Man's only hospice
OL,6,F"As part of this, some services
OL,7,Fincluding physiotherapy, occupational
OL,8,Ftherapy, psychological therapies and
OL,9,Flymphoedema services will transition
OL,10,Finto Manx Care and planning is already
OL,11,Funderway to make that transition safe
OL,12,Fand smooth for patients.
OL,14,F"To support Hospice during this
OL,15,Fperiod, Manx Care is working with
OL,16,FHospice to protect and maintain core
OL,17,Fservices, including Hospice at Home
OL,18,Fand specialist nursing care."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
